data.description: SOUTHERN CHARM at its finest!! This BEAUTIFUL property in South Lowndes County has it all!!! Almost 800ft of water frontage on OCEAN POND and almost 6 total acres. The view from the back porch overlooking the water is something you have to experience in person to appreciate. The outdoor space is PERFECT for entertaining and the LARGE GREAT ROOM transitions outdoor space to indoor space flawlessly. The natural lighting and unobstructed view of the pond make this great room a place you will never want to leave! In addition to the great room, you also have a smaller more quaint living room with a GAS FIREPLACE. This space would make a perfect sitting room or even a play room for the kids. The spacious bedrooms have all NEW CARPET and both full bathrooms have new LVP flooring. The kitchen has recently been spruced up with new paint and hardware on the cabinets. In addition to all the indoor living space, you also have plenty of room for storage and any toys! 2 car garage with 1/2 golf cart garage attached to the home as well as a MASSIVE shop/MAN CAVE which is detached. The man cave is 22x27 and insulated. The 2 garage spaces with roll up doors are 16x23 & 13x22 respectively. There is also an additional small shop area that measures 11x16.  The roof was replaced in 2021, new well tank, pump and piping was all replaced in 2020. New duct work in attic was done in 2022. This property is a must see! Call and schedule your showing today!!!!
